{"author":{"uri":{"label":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/reviews/id43570475"}, "name":{"label":"Chazho"}, "label":""}, "updated":{"label":"2025-03-16T09:33:55-07:00"}, "im:rating":{"label":"5"}, "im:version":{"label":"3.124.0"}, "id":{"label":"12428082140"}, "title":{"label":"Great app!"}, "content":{"label":"This app appears to send a photo of the receipt up to a server, where the OCR work is done. In any case, the result is exceptionally good and accurate processing. \n\nThen it's very easy to assign amounts to individual people, allocating expenses separately for each person.\n\nTIP: To assign the cost of an item to people: 1. Select the person first (not the item). 2. Then select all items for which the person will pay some or all of the cost. 3. Select another person, and do the same. If multiple people are signed to the same item, the cost is automatically divided!\n\nThe app allows you to add additional items, correct misinterpreted ones, enter any discounts, as well as specifying the amount of sales tax and the percent of tip. \n\nIf the check is handwritten, or there is any other reason that you need to enter all the amounts yourself, you can skip the photo and OCR, and enter the numbers manually.\n\nIt's all very easy, and the user interface is well done. I contacted technical support with a potential problem, and their responsiveness was excellent.", "attributes":{"type":"text"}}, "link":{"attributes":{"rel":"related", "href":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/review?id=595068606&type=Purple%20Software"}}, "im:voteSum":{"label":"0"}, "im:contentType":{"attributes":{"term":"Application", "label":"Application"}}, "im:voteCount":{"label":"1"}}, 
